    "description": "<strong>Dungeon Ward</strong>是一款融合了<strong>经典的基于网格的地牢探索游戏</strong>和快节奏的<strong>动作角色扮演游戏</strong>，提供激烈的<strong>实时战斗</strong>、战略性移动和角色养成。由独立开发者独自开发，Dungeon Ward以令人心跳加速的战斗为核心，重新点燃了90年代地牢探索的激情。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/af59fd9c57465f5347fb13514edb4fbf.poster.avif?t=1769119961\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/af59fd9c57465f5347fb13514edb4fbf.webm?t=1769119961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/af59fd9c57465f5347fb13514edb4fbf.mp4?t=1769119961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在三种独特职业中选择</h2> <strong>战士</strong>：拥有防御和攻击能力的坚韧近战战斗者。 <strong>弓箭手</strong>：擅长远程战斗，但也能变身为狼人，进行毁灭性的近战攻击。 <strong>法师</strong>：精通元素魔法，能够施放火球、闪电和其他强大的法术。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/6fdaaf0ef46b3bd527cf8361b1b1c603.poster.avif?t=1769119961\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/6fdaaf0ef46b3bd527cf8361b1b1c603.webm?t=1769119961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/6fdaaf0ef46b3bd527cf8361b1b1c603.mp4?t=1769119961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >学习特殊技能和天赋</h2> 投资于技能树和天赋点数，解锁强大的主动和被动能力，定制你的角色构建以适应你的游戏风格。无论你偏好纯粹的力量、致命的精准度，还是魔法造诣，选择权在你手中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/3a411234e32e374b037788beb67f14e1.poster.avif?t=1769119961\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/3a411234e32e374b037788beb67f14e1.webm?t=1769119961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/3a411234e32e374b037788beb67f14e1.mp4?t=1769119961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挑战强大的首领战</h2> 与史诗级的首领对决，每个首领都有独特的机制，需要策略和快速反应。时机把握、位置选择和对职业的精通是成功的关键。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/9d3f41d0d53ed1ed79edb579103b17e3.poster.avif?t=1769119961\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/9d3f41d0d53ed1ed79edb579103b17e3.webm?t=1769119961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/9d3f41d0d53ed1ed79edb579103b17e3.mp4?t=1769119961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >寻找史诗级战利品</h2> 在你穿越地牢的过程中收集强大的战利品，装备和物品都能满足你的职业和构建需求。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/be475f08e8d0e02fc32d4261c1f1d6c3.poster.avif?t=1769119961\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/be475f08e8d0e02fc32d4261c1f1d6c3.webm?t=1769119961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/be475f08e8d0e02fc32d4261c1f1d6c3.mp4?t=1769119961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >准备好体验经典地牢探索的新玩法了吗？</h2> 立即踏入Dungeon Ward，磨炼你的技能，征服充满致命敌人的危险地牢。你能否生存下来，成为一名英雄？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/2d473040914756823f0474d96fa02fa6.poster.avif?t=1769119961\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/2d473040914756823f0474d96fa02fa6.webm?t=1769119961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220150/extras/2d473040914756823f0474d96fa02fa6.mp4?t=1769119961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >立即将<strong>Dungeon Ward</strong>添加到您的<strong>愿望单</strong>，准备迎接一场史诗级的冒险！</h2>",
